                </span>
                <span class="content-container-2">
                    <p class="minor-expansion">IG: @rjcoalition, FB:  Restorative Justice Coalition</p>
                </span>
                <img src="/img/rjc.png" alt="a group of shapes within a triangle with the words Restorative Justice Coalition surrounding it">
                <span class="content-container-3 orchid-crayola">
                    <p>The <a href="https://www.restorativejusticecoalition.com">Restorative Justice Coalition</a> is a grassroots, community-based advocacy organization based in Tampa FL. Founded by Sadie (she/her) and Angel (he/him) in 2017, the organization focuses on challenging police violence and brutality, partnering with families impacted by such violence, participatory defense, local and state-level legislative policy, training, mentoring, and educating restorative justice practitioners and engaging in or consulting restorative justice processes. </p>
